transformations.description: This source query is a custom query that will combine data from our policy_risk_key_reference, risk_stg, addr_stg, building_stg, insured_stg, agents_detail_stg, master_agency_detail, agency_scores, insurancescore_stg, insurance_to_value_reference, uw_dashboard_betterview_details, and application_stg tables, along with the application-specific staging tables. The source query will be a union of policy and application data.
transformations.name: src_query

object.customQuery:
select
distinct prkr.policy_system_id,
prkr.policy_cmm_container,
prkr.policy_reference_id,
prkr.shell_policy_indicator,
prkr.policy_company,
prkr.policy_number,
prkr.policy_module_number,
prkr.policy_key,
prkr.policy_key_code,
prkr.line_system_id,
prkr.line_id,
prkr.line_of_business,
prkr.risk_system_id,
prkr.risk_id,
r.locationref as location_id,
r.totalannualsalesorrentalincome as total_annual_sales_or_rental_income,
case when a1.addr1 is not null then a1.systemid
when a2.addr1 is not null then a2.systemid
else null end as address_system_id,
case when a1.addr1 is not null then a1.addrtypecd
when a2.addr1 is not null then a2.addrtypecd
else null end as address_type_cd,
case when a1.addr1 is not null then a1.stateprovcd
when a2.addr1 is not null then a2.stateprovcd
else null end as risk_state,
sr.code as state_code,
case when a1.addr1 is not null
then ltrim(rtrim(coalesce(a1.addr1, '') || ' ' || coalesce(a1.addr2, '') || ' ' || coalesce(a1.addr3, '') || ' ' || coalesce(a1.addr4, '')))
when a2.addr1 is not null
then ltrim(rtrim(coalesce(a2.addr1, '') || ' ' || coalesce(a2.addr2, '') || ' ' || coalesce(a2.addr3, '') || ' ' || coalesce(a2.addr4, '')))
else null
end as risk_address,
case when a1.addr1 is not null then a1.postalcode
when a2.addr1 is not null then a2.postalcode
else null end as risk_zip_code,
case when a1.addr1 is not null
then ltrim(rtrim(coalesce(a1.county, '') || ' ' || coalesce(a1.stateprovcd)))
when a2.addr1 is not null
then ltrim(rtrim(coalesce(a2.county, '') || ' ' || coalesce(a2.stateprovcd)))
else null
end as risk_county,
case when a1.addr1 is not null then a1.city
when a2.addr1 is not null then a2.city
else null end as risk_city,
b.systemid as building_system_id,
coalesce(b.distancetocoastfeet, b.distancetocoastmile * 5280) as distance_to_coast_in_feet,
b.purchased_last_twelve_months as new_purchase,
b.wiringcd as wiring_status,
b.plumbingcd as plumbing_status,
b.heatingcd as heating_status,
b.roofingcd as roofing_status,
b.roofingyear as year_roofing_was_updated,
b.sqft as living_area_in_square_feet,
b.msbrctreconstructioncost as msb_replacement_cost_with_debris_removal,
b.accountcreditind as account_credit_indicator,
b.jewelrylimit as blanket_jewelry_schedule,
i.systemid as insured_system_id,
i.id as insured_id,
i.indexname as insured_name,
ad.systemid as agents_system_id,
ad.agencycd as agency_code,
ad.commercialname as agency_name,
mad.agency_appointed_dt as agency_appointed_date,
ags.agency_calibration_score as agency_score,
ags.agency_subjective_score as agency_subjective_score,
ins.systemid as insurance_score_system_id,
ins.insurancescore as policy_insurance_score_primary,
ins.currentscore as policy_insurance_score_secondary,
coalesce(itvr1.zip_code_average_cost_per_square_foot, itvr2.zip_code_average_cost_per_square_foot) as zip_code_average_cost_per_square_foot,
coalesce(itvr1.zip_code_square_feet_risk_count, itvr2.zip_code_square_feet_risk_count) as zip_code_square_feet_risk_count,
bv1.property_roof_spotlight_index,
bv1.building_area_in_square_feet,
bv1.building_number_of_dangerous_trees,
bv1.building_aggregate_tree_score,
bv1.detection_tree_overhang_in_square_feet,
bv2.detection_yard_debris_in_square_feet,
l.coveragetypecd,
r.typecd,
bp.subtypecd,
b.id as building_id,
tgt.uw_dashboard_policy_risk_details_row_id,
tgt.uw_dashboard_policy_risk_details_md5_hash_value,
  b.numoffamilies as number_of_families,
  b.protectionclass as protection_class,
  b.yearbuilt as year_built,
  b.h107ind as h107_indicator
from dbo.policy_risk_key_reference prkr
left join dbo.basicpolicy_stg bs 
on prkr.policy_system_id = bs.systemid 
and prkr.policy_cmm_container = bs.cmmcontainer 
and prkr.policy_reference_id = bs.id 
left join dbo.risk_stg r on
prkr.risk_system_id = r.systemid
and prkr.policy_cmm_container = r.cmmcontainer
and prkr.risk_id = r.id
left join dbo.building_stg b on
prkr.risk_system_id = b.systemid
and prkr.policy_cmm_container = b.cmmcontainer
and prkr.risk_id = b.parentid
left join dbo.addr_stg a1 on
b.systemid = a1.systemid
and b.cmmcontainer = a1.cmmcontainer
and b.id = a1.parentid
and a1.addrtypecd = 'RiskAddr'
and a1.addr1 is not null
and a1.stateprovcd in ('CT', 'MA', 'ME', 'NH', 'NY', 'NJ', 'IL', 'RI')
left join dbo.addr_stg a2 on
r.systemid = a2.systemid
and r.cmmcontainer = a2.cmmcontainer
and r.locationref = a2.parentid
and a2.addrtypecd = 'LocationAddr'
and a2.addr1 is not null
and a1.stateprovcd in ('CT', 'MA', 'ME', 'NH', 'NY', 'NJ', 'IL', 'RI')
left join dbo.insured_stg i on
prkr.policy_system_id = i.systemid
and prkr.policy_cmm_container = i.cmmcontainer
left join dbo.agents_detail_stg ad on
bs.providerref = ad.systemid
left join dbo.master_agency_detail mad on
ad.agencycd = mad.agency_code
and mad.row_end_dt = '9999-12-31'
left join dbo.agency_scores ags on
ad.agencycd = ags.agency_code
left join dbo.insurancescore_stg ins on
prkr.policy_system_id = ins.systemid
and prkr.policy_cmm_container = ins.cmmcontainer
and ins.insurancescoretypecd = 'InsuredInsuranceScore'
left join dbo.insurance_to_value_reference itvr1 on
left(a1.postalcode,5) = itvr1.zip_code
and prkr.line_of_business = itvr1.line_of_business 
left join dbo.insurance_to_value_reference itvr2 on
left(a2.postalcode,5) = itvr2.zip_code
and prkr.line_of_business = itvr2.line_of_business 
left join dbo.state_ref sr on
sr.riskstatelevel = case when a1.addr1 is not null then a1.stateprovcd
when a2.addr1 is not null then a2.stateprovcd
else null end 
left join dbo.line_stg l on
l.systemid = prkr.policy_system_id
and l.cmmcontainer = prkr.policy_cmm_container
left join dbo.basicpolicy_stg bp on
bp.systemid = prkr.policy_system_id
and bp.cmmcontainer = prkr.policy_cmm_container
left join (
select
distinct property_risk_id,
case
when detection_name = 'Overhang' then detection_area_in_square_feet
end as detection_tree_overhang_in_square_feet,
property_roof_spotlight_index,
building_aggregate_tree_score,
building_number_of_dangerous_trees,
building_area_in_square_feet,
rank() over (partition by property_risk_id order by
		property_latest_image_capture_date desc nulls last,
		property_completion_date_of_ordered_betterview_risk_data_pull desc nulls last,
		property_update_date desc nulls last,
		property_version_id desc nulls last) as rnk
from
dbo.uw_dashboard_betterview_details
where building_number = 1
and uw_dashboard_betterview_details_row_effective_end_date = '9999-12-31') bv1  on
bv1.property_risk_id = prkr.policy_number || '-' || prkr.policy_module_number 
and bv1.rnk = 1
left join (
select
distinct property_risk_id,
case
when detection_name = 'Yard Debris' then detection_area_in_square_feet
end as detection_yard_debris_in_square_feet,
rank() over (partition by property_risk_id order by
		property_latest_image_capture_date desc nulls last,
		property_completion_date_of_ordered_betterview_risk_data_pull desc nulls last,
		property_update_date desc nulls last,
		property_version_id desc nulls last) as rnk
from
dbo.uw_dashboard_betterview_details
where building_number = 0
and uw_dashboard_betterview_details_row_effective_end_date = '9999-12-31') bv2  on
bv2.property_risk_id = prkr.policy_number || '-' || prkr.policy_module_number 
and bv2.rnk = 1
left join dbo.uw_dashboard_policy_risk_details tgt
on prkr.policy_system_id = tgt.policy_system_id
and prkr.policy_cmm_container = tgt.policy_cmm_container
and prkr.risk_id = tgt.risk_id
and coalesce(b.id, '') = coalesce(tgt.building_id, '')
and coalesce(r.locationref, '') = coalesce(tgt.location_id, '')
and tgt.uw_dashboard_policy_risk_details_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31'
where
prkr.policy_risk_key_reference_row_effective_end_date = '9999-12-31'
and prkr.policy_cmm_container = 'Policy'

union

select
distinct prkr.policy_system_id,
prkr.policy_cmm_container,
prkr.policy_reference_id,
prkr.shell_policy_indicator,
prkr.policy_company,
prkr.policy_number,
prkr.policy_module_number,
prkr.policy_key,
prkr.policy_key_code,
prkr.line_system_id,
prkr.line_id,
prkr.line_of_business,
prkr.risk_system_id,
prkr.risk_id,
r.risk_application_location_ref as location_id,
r.total_annual_sales_or_rental_income as total_annual_sales_or_rental_income,
case when a1.address_application_address1 is not null then a1.address_application_system_id
when a2.address_application_address1 is not null then a2.address_application_system_id
else null end as address_system_id,
case when a1.address_application_address1 is not null then a1.address_application_address_type_cd
when a2.address_application_address1 is not null then a2.address_application_address_type_cd
else null end as address_type_cd,
case when a1.address_application_address1 is not null then a1.address_application_state_prov_cd
when a2.address_application_address1 is not null then a2.address_application_state_prov_cd
else null end as risk_state,
sr.code as state_code,
case when a1.address_application_address1 is not null 
then ltrim(rtrim(coalesce(a1.address_application_address1, '') || ' ' || coalesce(a1.address_application_address2, '') || ' ' || coalesce(a1.address_application_address3, '') || ' ' || coalesce(a1.address_application_address4, '')))
when a2.address_application_address1 is not null
then ltrim(rtrim(coalesce(a2.address_application_address1, '') || ' ' || coalesce(a2.address_application_address2, '') || ' ' || coalesce(a2.address_application_address3, '') || ' ' || coalesce(a2.address_application_address4, '')))
else null
end as risk_address,
case when a1.address_application_address1 is not null then a1.address_application_postal_code
when a2.address_application_address1 is not null then a2.address_application_postal_code
else null end as risk_zip_code,
case when a1.address_application_address1 is not null
then ltrim(rtrim(coalesce(a1.address_application_county, '') || ' ' || coalesce(a1.address_application_state_prov_cd)))
when a2.address_application_address1 is not null
then ltrim(rtrim(coalesce(a2.address_application_county, '') || ' ' || coalesce(a2.address_application_state_prov_cd)))
else null
end as risk_county,
case when a1.address_application_address1 is not null then a1.address_application_city
when a2.address_application_address1 is not null then a2.address_application_city
else null end as risk_city,
b.building_application_system_id as building_system_id,
coalesce(b.building_application_distance_to_coast_feet, b.building_application_distance_to_coast_mile * 5280) as distance_to_coast_in_feet,
b.building_application_purchased_last_twelve_months as new_purchase,
b.building_application_wiring_cd as wiring_status,
b.building_application_plumbing_cd as plumbing_status,
b.building_application_heating_cd as heating_status,
b.building_application_roofing_cd as roofing_status,
b.building_application_roofing_year as year_roofing_was_updated,
b.building_application_square_feet as living_area_in_square_feet,
b.building_application_msbrct_reconstruction_cost as msb_replacement_cost_with_debris_removal,
b.building_application_account_credit_ind as account_credit_indicator,
b.building_application_jewelry_limit as blanket_jewelry_schedule,
i.insured_application_system_id as insured_system_id,
i.insured_application_id as insured_id,
i.insured_application_index_name as insured_name,
ad.systemid as agents_system_id,
ad.agencycd as agency_code,
ad.commercialname as agency_name,
mad.agency_appointed_dt as agency_appointed_date,
ags.agency_calibration_score as agency_score,
ags.agency_subjective_score,
ins.systemid as insurance_score_system_id,
ins.insurancescore as policy_insurance_score_primary,
ins.currentscore as policy_insurance_score_secondary,
coalesce(itvr1.zip_code_average_cost_per_square_foot, itvr2.zip_code_average_cost_per_square_foot) as zip_code_average_cost_per_square_foot,
coalesce(itvr1.zip_code_square_feet_risk_count, itvr2.zip_code_square_feet_risk_count) as zip_code_square_feet_risk_count,
bv1.property_roof_spotlight_index,
bv1.building_area_in_square_feet,
bv1.building_number_of_dangerous_trees,
bv1.building_aggregate_tree_score,
bv1.detection_tree_overhang_in_square_feet,
bv2.detection_yard_debris_in_square_feet,
l.coveragetypecd,
r.risk_application_type_code,
bp.subtypecd,
b.building_application_id,
tgt.uw_dashboard_policy_risk_details_row_id,
tgt.uw_dashboard_policy_risk_details_md5_hash_value,
  b.building_application_number_of_families as number_of_families,
  b.building_application_protection_class as protection_class,
  b.building_application_year_built as year_built,
  b.building_application_h107_indicator as h107_indicator
from dbo.policy_risk_key_reference prkr
left join dbo.basicpolicyapp_stg bs 
on prkr.policy_system_id = bs.systemid 
and prkr.policy_cmm_container = bs.cmmcontainer 
and prkr.policy_reference_id = bs.id 
left join dbo.risk_application_stg r on
prkr.risk_system_id = r.risk_application_system_id
and prkr.policy_cmm_container = r.risk_application_cmm_container
and prkr.risk_id = r.risk_application_id
left join dbo.building_application_stg b on
prkr.risk_system_id = b.building_application_system_id
and prkr.policy_cmm_container = b.building_application_cmm_container
and prkr.risk_id = b.building_application_parent_id
left join dbo.address_application_stg a1 on
b.building_application_system_id = a1.address_application_system_id
and b.building_application_cmm_container = a1.address_application_cmm_container
and b.building_application_id = a1.address_application_parent_id
and a1.address_application_address_type_cd = 'RiskAddr'
and a1.address_application_address1 is not null
and a1.address_application_state_prov_cd in ('CT', 'MA', 'ME', 'NH', 'NY', 'NJ', 'IL', 'RI')
left join dbo.address_application_stg a2 on
r.risk_application_system_id = a2.address_application_system_id
and r.risk_application_cmm_container = a2.address_application_cmm_container
and r.risk_application_location_ref = a2.address_application_parent_id
and a2.address_application_address_type_cd = 'LocationAddr'
and a2.address_application_address1 is not null
and a2.address_application_state_prov_cd in ('CT', 'MA', 'ME', 'NH', 'NY', 'NJ', 'IL', 'RI')
left join dbo.insured_application_stg i on
prkr.policy_system_id = i.insured_application_system_id
and prkr.policy_system_id = i.insured_application_cmm_container
left join dbo.agents_detail_stg ad on
bs.providerref = ad.systemid
left join dbo.master_agency_detail mad on
ad.agencycd = mad.agency_code
and mad.row_end_dt = '9999-12-31'
left join dbo.agency_scores ags on
ad.agencycd = ags.agency_code
left join dbo.insurancescore_stg ins on
prkr.policy_system_id = ins.systemid
and prkr.policy_cmm_container = ins.cmmcontainer
and ins.insurancescoretypecd = 'InsuredInsuranceScore'
left join dbo.insurance_to_value_reference itvr1 on
left(a1.address_application_postal_code,5) = itvr1.zip_code
and prkr.line_of_business = itvr1.line_of_business 
left join dbo.insurance_to_value_reference itvr2 on
left(a2.address_application_postal_code,5) = itvr2.zip_code
and prkr.line_of_business = itvr2.line_of_business 
left join (
select
distinct property_risk_id,
case
when detection_name = 'Overhang' then detection_area_in_square_feet
end as detection_tree_overhang_in_square_feet,
property_roof_spotlight_index,
building_aggregate_tree_score,
building_number_of_dangerous_trees,
building_area_in_square_feet,
rank() over (partition by property_risk_id order by
		property_latest_image_capture_date desc nulls last,
		property_completion_date_of_ordered_betterview_risk_data_pull desc nulls last,
		property_update_date desc nulls last,
		property_version_id desc nulls last) as rnk
from
dbo.uw_dashboard_betterview_details
where building_number = 1
and uw_dashboard_betterview_details_row_effective_end_date = '9999-12-31') bv1  on
bv1.property_risk_id = prkr.policy_number || '-' || prkr.policy_module_number 
and bv1.rnk = 1
left join (
select
distinct property_risk_id,
case
when detection_name = 'Yard Debris' then detection_area_in_square_feet
end as detection_yard_debris_in_square_feet,
rank() over (partition by property_risk_id order by
		property_latest_image_capture_date desc nulls last,
		property_completion_date_of_ordered_betterview_risk_data_pull desc nulls last,
		property_update_date desc nulls last,
		property_version_id desc nulls last) as rnk
from
dbo.uw_dashboard_betterview_details
where building_number = 0
and uw_dashboard_betterview_details_row_effective_end_date = '9999-12-31') bv2  on
bv2.property_risk_id = prkr.policy_number || '-' || prkr.policy_module_number 
and bv2.rnk = 1
left join dbo.state_ref sr on
sr.riskstatelevel = case when a1.address_application_address1 is not null then a1.address_application_state_prov_cd
when a2.address_application_address1 is not null then a2.address_application_state_prov_cd
else null end
left join dbo.line_stg l on
l.systemid = prkr.policy_system_id
and l.cmmcontainer = prkr.policy_cmm_container
left join dbo.basicpolicyapp_stg bp on
bp.systemid = prkr.policy_system_id
and bp.cmmcontainer = prkr.policy_cmm_container
left join dbo.uw_dashboard_policy_risk_details tgt
on prkr.policy_system_id = tgt.policy_system_id
and prkr.policy_cmm_container = tgt.policy_cmm_container
and prkr.risk_id = tgt.risk_id
and coalesce(b.building_application_id, '') = coalesce(tgt.building_id, '')
and coalesce(r.risk_application_location_ref, '') = coalesce(tgt.location_id, '')
and tgt.uw_dashboard_policy_risk_details_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31'
where
prkr.policy_risk_key_reference_row_effective_end_date = '9999-12-31'
and prkr.policy_cmm_container = 'Application'

attributes.name: Download S3 Files In Multiple Parts

transformations.description: This expression will set the fields needed to be used for audit, such as the effective dates. This will also calculate the md5 hash value for comparisons and the policy_base_form. We will also format the risk county and risk state fields.
transformations.name: exp_set_audit_fields_and_calculations

fields.name: src_md5_hash_value
fields.expression:
MD5('policy_system_id' || TO_CHAR(policy_system_id) ||
'policy_cmm_container' || policy_cmm_container || 
'policy_reference_id' || policy_reference_id || 
'shell_policy_indicator' || shell_policy_indicator || 
'policy_company' || policy_company || 
'policy_number' || policy_number || 
'policy_module_number' || policy_module_number || 
'policy_key' || policy_key ||
'policy_key_code' || policy_key_code ||
'line_system_id' || TO_CHAR(line_system_id) ||
'line_id' || line_id ||
'line_of_business' || line_of_business ||
'risk_system_id' || TO_CHAR(risk_system_id) ||
'risk_id' || risk_id ||
'location_id' || location_id ||
'total_annual_sales_or_rental_income' || TO_CHAR(total_annual_sales_or_rental_income) ||
'address_system_id' || TO_CHAR(address_system_id) ||
'address_type_cd' || address_type_cd ||
'risk_state' || risk_state ||
'state_code' || state_code ||
'risk_address' || risk_address ||
'risk_zip_code' || risk_zip_code ||
'risk_county' || risk_county ||
'risk_city' || risk_city ||
'building_system_id' || TO_CHAR(building_system_id) ||
'distance_to_coast_in_feet' || TO_CHAR(distance_to_coast_in_feet) ||
'new_purchase' || new_purchase ||
'wiring_status' || wiring_status ||
'plumbing_status' || plumbing_status ||
'heating_status' || heating_status ||
'roofing_status' || roofing_status ||
'year_roofing_was_updated' || year_roofing_was_updated ||
'living_area_in_square_feet' || TO_CHAR(living_area_in_square_feet) ||
'msb_replacement_cost_with_debris_removal' || msb_replacement_cost_with_debris_removal ||
'account_credit_indicator' || account_credit_indicator ||
'blanket_jewelry_schedule' || blanket_jewelry_schedule ||
'insured_system_id' || TO_CHAR(insured_system_id) ||
'insured_id' || insured_id ||
'insured_name' || insured_name ||
'agents_system_id' || agents_system_id ||
'agency_code' || agency_code ||
'agency_name' || agency_name ||
'agency_appointed_date' || TO_CHAR(agency_appointed_date) ||
'agency_score' || TO_CHAR(agency_score) ||
'agency_subjective_score' || TO_CHAR(agency_subjective_score) ||
'insurance_score_system_id' || TO_CHAR(insurance_score_system_id) ||
'policy_insurance_score_primary' || policy_insurance_score_primary ||
'policy_insurance_score_secondary' || policy_insurance_score_secondary || 
'zip_code_average_cost_per_square_foot' || TO_CHAR(zip_code_average_cost_per_square_foot) ||
'zip_code_square_feet_risk_count' || TO_CHAR(zip_code_square_feet_risk_count) ||
'property_roof_spotlight_index' || TO_CHAR(property_roof_spotlight_index) ||
'building_area_in_square_feet' || TO_CHAR(building_area_in_square_feet) ||
'building_number_of_dangerous_trees' || TO_CHAR(building_number_of_dangerous_trees) ||
'building_aggregate_tree_score' || TO_CHAR(building_aggregate_tree_score) ||
'detection_tree_overhang_in_square_feet' || TO_CHAR(detection_tree_overhang_in_square_feet) ||
'detection_yard_debris_in_square_feet' || TO_CHAR(detection_yard_debris_in_square_feet) ||
'coveragetypecd' || coveragetypecd ||
'typecd' || typecd ||
'subtypecd' || subtypecd ||
'building_id' || building_id
)

fields.name: o_risk_state
fields.expression:
IIF(ISNULL(risk_state) or ISNULL(state_code), NULL, 
risk_state || ' (' || state_code || ')')

fields.name: o_risk_county
fields.expression:
IIF(ISNULL(risk_county) or ISNULL(state_code), NULL,
risk_county || ' (' || state_code || ')')

fields.name: policy_base_form
fields.expression:
IIF(IN(v_TypeCD,'BOP', 'BOP1'), 'Standard',
IIF(v_TypeCD = 'BOP2', 'Special',
IIF(v_TypeCD = 'ExcessLiability' OR v_TypeCD='Businessowners Excess Liability', 'Excess',
IIF(v_TypeCD = 'UmbrellaLiability' OR  v_TypeCD='Businessowners Umbrella Liability','Commercial Umbrella',
IIF(v_TypeCD = 'UmbrellaBasic', 'PersonalUmbrella', v_TypeCD)))))
